** Avy

Avy is used to jump between points in Emacs. [[http://pragmaticemacs.com/emacs/super-efficient-movement-using-avy/][Here's]] the source of the key combination.

#+begin_src emacs-lisp
(use-package avy
  :ensure t
  :bind (("M-s" . avy-goto-word-1)))
#+end_src

#+RESULTS:
